Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}什麼是所謂希望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\fs40\shad0\blur3\bord1\pos(1077.334,633.334)}和敵人中樞的星核對話
